      <title class="- topic/title " xtrc="title:2;18:14" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/colspec.dita">Attributes</title>
      <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:1;19:10" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/colspec.dita">The following attributes are available on this element: <xref class="- topic/xref " href="../attributes/universalAttributes.dita" keyref="attributes-universal" xtrc="xref:1;20:42" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/colspec.dita" type="reference"><?ditaot gentext?>Universal attribute group<?ditaot genshortdesc?><desc class="- topic/desc ">The universal attribute group defines a set of common attributes available on most DITA     elements. The universal attribute group includes all attributes from the metadata, ID,     localization, and debug attribute groups, plus the <xmlatt class="+ topic/keyword markup-d/markupname xml-d/xmlatt " xtrc="xmlatt:1;8:64" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/attributes/universalAttributes.dita">class</xmlatt> attribute.</desc></xref> (without the Metadata attribute group),
          <xmlatt class="+ topic/keyword markup-d/markupname xml-d/xmlatt " xtrc="xmlatt:1;21:19" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/colspec.dita">base</xmlatt> from the <xref class="- topic/xref " href="../attributes/metadataAttributes.dita" keyref="attributes-metadata" xtrc="xref:2;21:78" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/colspec.dita" type="reference"><?ditaot gentext?>Metadata attribute group<?ditaot genshortdesc?><desc class="- topic/desc ">The metadata attribute group includes common metadata attributes, several of which     support conditional processing (filtering and flagging) or the creation of new attribute domain     specializations.</desc></xref>, and the attributes
        defined below. This element also uses <xmlatt class="+ topic/keyword markup-d/markupname xml-d/xmlatt " xtrc="xmlatt:2;22:55" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/colspec.dita">align</xmlatt>, <xmlatt class="+ topic/keyword markup-d/markupname xml-d/xmlatt " xtrc="xmlatt:3;22:79" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/colspec.dita">char</xmlatt>,
          <xmlatt class="+ topic/keyword markup-d/markupname xml-d/xmlatt " xtrc="xmlatt:4;23:19" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/colspec.dita">charoff</xmlatt>, <xmlatt class="+ topic/keyword markup-d/markupname xml-d/xmlatt " xtrc="xmlatt:5;23:45" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/colspec.dita">colsep</xmlatt>, <xmlatt class="+ topic/keyword markup-d/markupname xml-d/xmlatt " xtrc="xmlatt:6;23:70" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/colspec.dita">rowsep</xmlatt>, and
          <xmlatt class="+ topic/keyword markup-d/markupname xml-d/xmlatt " xtrc="xmlatt:7;24:19" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/colspec.dita">rowheader</xmlatt> from <xref class="- topic/xref " href="../attributes/calsTableAttributes.dita" keyref="attributes-calsTable" xtrc="xref:3;24:80" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/colspec.dita" type="reference"><?ditaot gentext?>Complex-table attribute group<?ditaot genshortdesc?><desc class="- topic/desc ">The Complex-table attribute group includes several attributes that are defined on   complex table elements. Most of these attributes are part of the OASIS Exchange model; table   elements generally use only a subset of the attributes defined in this group. These attributes are   not available for the <xmlelement class="+ topic/keyword markup-d/markupname xml-d/xmlelement " xtrc="xmlelement:1;9:37" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/attributes/calsTableAttributes.dita">simpletable</xmlelement> elements.</desc></xref>.</p>
