          <dd class="- topic/dd " xtrc="dd:1;28:15" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/colspec.dita">Indicates the number of a column in the table, counting from the first logical column
            to the last column.</dd>
        </dlentry>
